sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(Data Scientist)
    participant LS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Inference<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant VecDB as Vector DB<br/>(Milvus/pgvector/Qdrant)
    participant FMS as TrustyAI FMS<br/>Safety Orchestrator
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Chat Completion Request (vLLM backend)
    Client->>LS: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP, No Auth (platform handles)
    LS->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Bearer Token
    vLLM-->>LS: Completion Response
    LS->>PG: Log inference request/response<br/>PostgreSQL, Password Auth
    PG-->>LS: OK
    LS-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTP

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: RAG Query with Vector Search
    Client->>LS: POST /v1/agents/*<br/>HTTP, No Auth
    LS->>VecDB: Vector similarity search<br/>REST/gRPC/PostgreSQL<br/>API Key/Password
    VecDB-->>LS: Relevant chunks
    LS->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>with context<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Bearer Token
    vLLM-->>LS: Augmented response
    LS->>PG: Log agent state + inference<br/>PostgreSQL, Password
    PG-->>LS: OK
    LS-->>Client: RAG Response<br/>HTTP

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Evaluation via Kubeflow Pipeline (RAGAS remote)
    Client->>LS: POST /v1/eval/*<br/>HTTP, No Auth
    LS->>KFP: Submit evaluation pipeline<br/>HTTP, Bearer Token
    KFP->>S3: Store/retrieve evaluation data<br/>HTTPS, AWS IAM
    S3-->>KFP: Dataset
    KFP->>LS: Callback with results<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    LS-->>Client: Evaluation Results<br/>HTTP

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: Safety Check via TrustyAI FMS
    Client->>LS: POST /v1/safety/*<br/>HTTP, No Auth
    LS->>FMS: Shield evaluation request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Configurable SSL
    FMS-->>LS: Safety verdict
    LS-->>Client: Safety Result<br/>HTTP
